":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"我會繼續和理非地癱瘓機場 做好文宣 諗下佔機場嘅初衷係咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">核彈都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"ba0d5090b9caff24e4c66247d7e3bb7a1294a60d","tid":1463603,"uid":121810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"[quote]我會繼續去 做好文宣 諗下佔機場嘅初衷係咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">核彈都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"850d8f28487cb03dbeea92008090f13e3531b8a3","tid":1463603,"uid":201146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467129/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467129/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n推呢個 <br />\n我係在場人士！！ 有簡易timeline！！ 聽日唔好答錯！"},{"pid":"2a5be8bf9ecc89597726fcdbeb66043c25cac125","tid":1463603,"uid":34191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f49a53fd1eb51f28408f76aa92d7522d1cef2c9","tid":1463603,"uid":121810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"我會繼續和理非地癱瘓機場 做好文宣 諗下佔機場嘅初衷係咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">核彈都唔割</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"如果我話有人入機場嘅初衷係癱瘓機場呢<br />\n<br />\n現實係 有一班人result oriented<br />\n而且覺得有迫切性<br />\n唔係話唔夠人就做文宣<br />\n所以癱瘓機場有用佢哋就會想每日都癱<br />\n<br />\n如果想和理非落去<br />\n就要諗方法用和理非嘅手段達到大家嘅目的<br />\n唔會全部人嘅初衷都係一致<br />\n但大家要做嘅係<br />\n令個結果變成你想要嘅畫面<br />\n<br />\n想和理非嘅<br />\n記得叫齊人 將個場變成和理非<br />\n<br />\n聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfc28dcf9ad69818de0cc5c1c2ad970659e7378","tid":1463603,"uid":293506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6be63e8f1a6b735468a1a6818123fe43133cb0fd","tid":1463603,"uid":34191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cfc28dcf9ad69818de0cc5c1c2ad970659e7378","tid":1463603,"uid":293506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61e6613b45ec583a3394b3ff9f144901d0c73f0","tid":1463603,"uid":255162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:47.000Z","msg":"好認同要多文宣為行動正名，等其他人理解。特別今日衝突畫面都真係有啲難睇。"},{"pid":"782afaa81bd613920702ced700fb9fdccf2dcd4d","tid":1463603,"uid":270733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:58.000Z","msg":"機師罷工會唔會道歉啊？！"},{"pid":"3475dd83e19d73fcffe723de9cbc716aa3b92274","tid":1463603,"uid":34191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d61e6613b45ec583a3394b3ff9f144901d0c73f0","tid":1463603,"uid":255162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:47.000Z","msg":"好認同要多文宣為行動正名，等其他人理解。特別今日衝突畫面都真係有啲難睇。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"其實有一樣嘢真係好難睇嘅<br />\n<br />\n假使大家話想為香港爭取民主自由<br />\n迫不得已要擺旅客上枱<br />\n但同一時間好多香港人會因為種種原因而唔去機場 連機場都塞唔滿<br />\n變相甚至乎唔關事嘅外國人 付出仲要比大部份香港人多<br />\n呢個係點都講唔過去<br />\n究竟仲點可以話呢個係大多數嘅意願？<br />\n<br />\n所以我真係好希望 只能承受和理非抗爭嘅大家<br />\n用行動去證明香港人係迫不得已先咁做<br />\n<br />\n如果夠人嘅 其實又點會有今日類似嘅衝突呢？<br />\n<br />\np.s. 那邊廂出咗禁令，希望大家唔好令我失望，我哋依家手握嘅，係一張叫癱瘓機場嘅王牌，但再唔用，好快就冇得用。<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3022668/riot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3022668%2Friot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Br3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=bae0bc7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3022668/riot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong</a>"},{"pid":"5cd7dc3ccecaf5024dccbc86432dab2e0ad0546e","tid":1463603,"uid":34191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"782afaa81bd613920702ced700fb9fdccf2dcd4d","tid":1463603,"uid":270733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:58.000Z","msg":"機師罷工會唔會道歉啊？！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"唔明 可唔可以elaborate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}